### Determine Appropriate Topics

**Required base topics:**
- `launchdarkly` - Always include
- `launchdarkly-labs` - Always include for Labs projects
- `feature-flags` + `feature-toggles` - Always pair together for SDK-related repos

**Category topics (choose appropriate):**
- `launchdarkly-sdk` - Official SDKs
- `launchdarkly-sdk-component` - SDK add-ons, integrations, shared libraries
- `launchdarkly-integration` - External tool integrations (IDE, CI/CD, build tools)
- `launchdarkly-api` - API clients
- `launchdarkly-docker-image` - Docker images
- `launchdarkly-ai` - AI-related projects

**Technology topics:**

Languages (use variants):
- `go`, `golang` (both)
- `javascript`, `typescript` (both if applicable)
- `node`, `nodejs`, `node-js` (all three for Node)
- `react`, `reactjs`, `react-js` (all three for React)
- `csharp`, `c-sharp`, `dotnet` (all three for .NET)
- `python`, `ruby`, `java`, `rust`, `swift`, `php`, `dart`, etc.

Platforms/Frameworks:
- `angular`, `vue`, `flutter`, `electron`, `gatsby`
- `android`, `ios`, `macos`, `tvos`, `watchos`

Tools/Integrations:
- `cli`, `command-line-interface`
- `github-action`, `github-actions`, `actions` (all three for GitHub Actions)
- `terraform`, `helm`, `helm-chart`
- `vscode`, `vscode-extension`
- `homebrew`, `homebrew-tap`, `brew`

Specialized:
- `sdk` - For all SDK repos
- `sdk-examples`, `examples` - For example repos
